5 WHEREAS, constructing a roundabout on LA-1019 near Old LA-16 would serve to
6 enhance driver and pedestrian safety.
7 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
8 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby urge and request the Department of Transportation and
9 Development to construct a roundabout on LA-1019 near Old LA-16.
10 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
11 secretary of the Department of Transportation and Development.
